Class DBBNodeComparator1LvlBndCstComb

  • java.lang.Object
    • graph.packing.DBBNodeComparator1LvlBndCstComb
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DBBNodeComparatorIntf, java.io.Serializable

    public class DBBNodeComparator1LvlBndCstComb
extends java.lang.Object
implements DBBNodeComparatorIntf
    Level-dependent Search for the Max Weighted Independent Set problem (MWIS). The comparison between two BB-nodes of type DBBNode0 only is via the "value" of each node, that is however dependent on the level of the node: below a threshold level, value is the DBBNode0's cost (total weight), whereas after that threshold level, value is the bound of the node.
